videos.description: In the final seconds of the game, UCLA's Bryce Alford hits the step back three to win the game for the Bruins' to capture their second top-10 upset at Pauley Pavillion this season.
videos.headline: Alford's last second shot upsets Arizona

videos.description: Bryce Alford talks to Bill Walton and Dave Pasch after hitting the game winner for UCLA with Russell Westbrook in attendance.
videos.headline: Alford loves having Westbrook in the building

videos.description: Bill Walton and Dave Pasch break down Bryce Alford's winning shot to knock off Arizona.
videos.headline: How Alford won the game
